==Mandarin==
'''一点儿''' is only used in Beijing. Outside Beijing instead is used '''一点''' (without the '''儿''') but with same meaning and pronunciation.
* '''Romanizations'''
*: '''[[Pinyin]]''': yī diăn ér (dian+er=diar)

